Welcome to the Mob!

  This help system is designed to give you the maximum possible amount
  of information to learn everything about this fine organization that
  you have joined.  Help is available on a variety of topics and may
  be accessed using 'mhelp <topic>'.

  If you think there needs to be an additional topic, more information
  on an existing topic, or if you notice a typo, please send mail to
  Cosmo or Languilen.

